{"tid":1895163,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（重製測試版）互動遊戲 《假如疫情惡化 人類變異》","createTime":"2020-02-24T11:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T08:49:33.000Z","uid":211347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"61c5b72904a826e80c3ba6fe5db35da0fe188514","tid":1895163,"uid":211347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:25:28.000Z","msg":"上一次冇講清楚個形式所以有啲誤會<br />\n喺度講返聲對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個形式其實就係你揀一個出身點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就設計自己嘅人物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後我就會畫個結局俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上一次好多巴絲打一開波就死咗 今集不如睇下啲人有冇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲留言一齊玩啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/inZkP-fY7Ss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FinZkP-fY7Ss&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=fefe040c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/inZkP-fY7Ss</a><br />\n<br />\n其實依個頻道係新開嘅 希望大家多多支持訂閱我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主要係用我哋嘅母語廣東話配音 再加動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲咩意見都可以喺下面講返 我哋會參考同改進<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5ae63829e431da1b9a84343588d7c102c62a65","tid":1895163,"uid":211347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:27:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e547ae8702fa1499c50a256e7a00c2209695c01","tid":1895163,"uid":8131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:28:05.000Z","msg":"大力一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de9c14d1b60ddc9136b98a4de277d3cdbd770b4","tid":1895163,"uid":211347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:28:08.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"d12f97f6c5c07353